------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bundled third-party code
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

lib/src/dagre/ contains a vendored copy of dart_dagre 1.0.0
(https://pub.dev/packages/dart_dagre), a Dart port of dagre.js
(https://github.com/dagrejs/dagre). This code is licensed under the
Apache License, Version 2.0; the full license text is in
lib/src/dagre/LICENSE.

It provides the generic layered-graph primitives (cycle breaking, ranking,
crossing minimization, Brandes–Köpf coordinate assignment, dummy-node
normalization, and compound/cluster handling) on top of which the ELK-style
orchestration, spacing model, and orthogonal edge routing in this package are
built. Local modifications (pure-Dart geometry types, import paths) are noted
in the source headers.
